comments.author: KingsDen
comments.body: Firstly, pump and dump is not a good way to earn money in trading. It is just like a rob Peter and pay Paul kind of scheme. And it is not ethical to involve yourself with such a scheme.Secondly, the people who gave out this time must have already occupied the bottom and before everyone could join and pump upto 30mins, they will take profit and dump the coin on you. Do not even take the risk to enter the market earlier because the pump might not happen at all.Thirdly, for a pump to be effective, it should be organised by a single or limited group with big numerical strength. Pump is not achieved by sharing the few unreliable information randomly on the internet.

comments.author: Bitcoin_Arena
comments.body: Classic pump and dump scam, and it's an old trick we know here. It was rife during the 2017 bull run period, and Bittrex was the exchange this pump and dump scammer would mostly use. The trick is, they buy the coins in advance and then announce that the coin is going to pump at a specific time. When the time arrives, gullible people rush to buy the coins because of FOMO and in the due process, the scammers unload the useless shitcoin on them and then move on to the next one.
